{"tid":1650483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教大家用 Citymapper輕鬆罷搭黨鐵","createTime":"2019-10-13T03:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T03:54:32.000Z","uid":281417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac50b38308f575de9bfa51abebe35910de85cadc","tid":1650483,"uid":281417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:43:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191013/60141683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191013%2F60141683&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=f3c2857a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191013%2F60141683&h=4521361d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191013/60141683</a><br />\n<br />\n【路線任揀】《Citymapper》交通工具App實測 飛走港鐵只搭巴士轉車返工無難度<br />\n<br />\n之前好多人都會依賴港鐵出出入入，記者都一樣，工作時四處去，很多時候都會乘搭港鐵。不過現時港鐵站隨時會關站，港鐵又隨時會停駛，好多人近期都用上《Citymapper》這款交通工具導航App搵車搭。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能會問Google Maps都有交通工具路線，《Citymapper》又有甚麼不同？Google Maps設有自行開車及步行建議，而《Citymapper》就比較着重公共交通工具，有鐵路、巴士、小巴、小輪等建議，亦有詳細的轉車路線及所需時間，甚至可選定單一交通工具轉乘都得，而且交通服務受阻如港鐵暫停服務都有顯示，在當下環境更好用。<br />\n記者在旺角街頭實測以《Citymapper》所建議的路線返回將軍澳工業邨公司，測試當日旺角站仍然封站，所以《Citymapper》App第一個選項港鐵轉巴士的路線根本毋須考慮。記者就揀選只以巴士作交通工具的選擇，當中最快路線是：先乘搭2X巴士線到新蒲崗譽港灣，再轉乘796X巴士到將軍澳工業邨電視城，再步行回蘋果日報。<br />\n<br />\n《Citymapper》最初建議時間是79分鐘，但記者跟着這條路線包括等車、步行時間在內，只需時70分鐘，比預期時間更快，跟以前乘搭港鐵再轉乘公司巴士返工相差無幾。《Citymapper》App更可預先設定公司及家中的地址，以後身處何地，都可快速搵到返工返屋企的交通路線，港鐵停駛都無有怕。"},{"pid":"d33990459eed558b4d0306adac4ef48d94db0103","tid":1650483,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnAJUrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnAJUrV.jpg&h=222a48c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>10.13 10.14 不見不散</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"667fd9c4c608e7172ff2b8b5101be59487462b52","tid":1650483,"uid":297334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esbX1iL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FesbX1iL.png&h=28b48a65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xYfNYL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xYfNYL.png&h=a2c33757&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5wX1iN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5wX1iN.png&h=1d7f3f6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bd56345e81583c6c16d9297286450f4366e31f0","tid":1650483,"uid":78513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:51:53.000Z","msg":"睇唔睇到塞車？"},{"pid":"416e435b238afe0b5e7c3fdacf3346acf9290130","tid":1650483,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"刪咗黨鐵apps<br />\n裝Citymapper 冇廣告 介面又正<br />\n<br />\n不過佢介紹嘅坐法都唔係最理想<br />\n<br />\n坐開巴士轉巴士嘅我<br />\n有咁多年經驗得出最直接最慳時間嘅組合"}]}